Acetone added to plasma so protein precipitates out, and supernatant is ran on NMR.
Frozen tissue is ground in a SPEX grinder under liquid nitrogen to homogenize the sample.
Lipid extraction from homogenate.
Polar extraction from homogenate.
Protein extraction and quantification.
Tissue is frozen in liquid nitrogen to stop metabolic processes.
